{"tid":940860,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"地圓說發表前地球叫咩","createTime":"2018-12-14T09:25:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T11:11:48.000Z","uid":201671,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1d644d165916e2ebe6d92ef1e8da2a49a9948f3c","tid":940860,"uid":201671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T09:25:14.000Z","msg":"以前嘅人一直以為地球係平<br />\n咁佢哋點叫地球<br />\n地板？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好覆我眼鏡蛇飯剷頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e6dc66ec3d5c83c4988a02711d4a0542dde87d1","tid":940860,"uid":59192,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T09:26:35.000Z","msg":"earth"},{"pid":"8165aa8288f0a1289112773508f9a717b0bda259","tid":940860,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T09:27:14.000Z","msg":"吾<br />\n系<br />\n甘<br />\n牙<br />\n挽<br />\n左<br />\n既<br />\n野<br />\n巧<br />\n令<br />\nX<br />\nD"},{"pid":"91ad912771e3c15d717a7b0138bc59b5e143b89a","tid":940860,"uid":3304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T09:27:47.000Z","msg":"中原"},{"pid":"a0fc3daedde8df88fc2601911b31ff3302755433","tid":940860,"uid":61954,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"91ad912771e3c15d717a7b0138bc59b5e143b89a","tid":940860,"uid":3304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T09:27:47.000Z","msg":"中原"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T09:29:12.000Z","msg":"地產"},{"pid":"927389ed2e23462e5fb82b41923c15c281066ff3","tid":940860,"uid":20867,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T09:32:16.000Z","msg":"地球的英文名「Earth」源自中古英語[n 6]，其歷史可追溯到古英語（時常作「eor&eth;e」）[49]，在日耳曼語族諸語中都有同源詞，其原始日耳曼語詞根構擬為「*er&thorn;ō」。拉丁文稱之為「Terra」，此為古羅馬神話中大地女神之名[50]。希臘文中則稱之為「&Gamma;&alpha;ῖ&alpha;」（Gaia），這個名稱是希臘神話中大地女神蓋亞的名字[51]。<br />\n<br />\n中文「地球」一詞最早出現於明朝的西學東漸時期，最早引入該詞的是義大利傳教士利瑪竇（Matteo Ricci，1552－1610），他於《坤輿萬國全圖》中使用了該詞[52][53]。清朝後期，西方近代科學引入中國，地圓說逐漸為中國人所接受，「地球」一詞（亦作「地毬」）被廣泛使用[54][55][56]，申報在創刊首月即登載《地球說》一文。[57]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/地球\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%83&d=fPCWDw3FhU9n97cnZSL7WL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=3690c2bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/地球</a>"},{"pid":"f9dc5e803c9f7e66b01297f1189132edde1aa0b0","tid":940860,"uid":36441,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T09:34:21.000Z","msg":"我哋嘅屋企就叫做地平<br />\n地球係圓嘅機會係零"},{"pid":"1a6b4b1a91de58ca6c2f9912cf8edbdabd127f47","tid":940860,"uid":81094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T09:36:14.000Z","msg":"米德加爾特"},{"pid":"279aadddd2d168363511b7d3583635ed8227e659","tid":940860,"uid":223816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T09:37:53.000Z","msg":"地板"},{"pid":"914c3fddba9610b4331801fc6a9b66c9d918cbc9","tid":940860,"uid":72713,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T09:39:34.000Z","msg":"地圖<br />\n你攞張世界地圖出黎睇，<br />\n其實係以前啲人的世界觀黎"},{"pid":"8d7c7c55ae48dc27cc4d44e05dda0781d5e6ee18","tid":940860,"uid":69168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T09:39:49.000Z","msg":"就咁叫大地，土地囉"},{"pid":"e26ada732f12ab13ed6acce68f768c899acc25c6","tid":940860,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T09:40:27.000Z","msg":"世界囉 屌你老母 咁撚蠢 係咪讀ive 架"},{"pid":"417a67cdc5fbc3f7ec0a3b87d257ac687464c400","tid":940860,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T09:40:30.000Z","msg":"地表"},{"pid":"3eb26771b799ffd31ad3344237af95bd5f6eb3bc","tid":940860,"uid":125030,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T09:43:06.000Z","msg":"天下"},{"pid":"d6c1c3d4aa90f949bbc5977434f836f95982d479","tid":940860,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T09:51:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c716676719fed7a38dad1c6